definition: primal chaos/formless mass before creation in Chinese mythology/muddled/innocent as a baby
to mix/to mingle/muddled/to drift along/to muddle along/to pass for/to get along with sb/thoughtless/reckless

sentences.english: This almost-falling into chaos keeps life proliferating.
sentences.chinese: 这种几近坠落乃至混沌的运行状态确保了生命的增殖。
褪尽红尘万物，自混沌中走来。

sentences.english: How can you sort out the order from the chaos?
sentences.chinese: 如何才能从混沌世界中理出头绪来呢？

sentences.english: This study made an attempt for chaotic anti-control application in the ocean reconnaissance robot.
sentences.chinese: 为混沌反控制在海洋侦察机器人的应用做了尝试。

sentences.english: Whole developing process of the intermittent chaos is described in more detail.
sentences.chinese: 本文较详细地描绘了阵发混沌发展的全过程。

sentences.english: The next few months passed in a blur.
sentences.chinese: 接下来的几个月混混沌沌地过去。

sentences.english: In chapter 3, The properties of chaotic group actions are considered.
sentences.chinese: 第三章，考虑离散群的混沌作用。

sentences.english: You wake me up, from profound coma and aimlessness.
sentences.chinese: 是你，将我从深深的混沌与迷惘中唤醒。

sentences.english: The spirit that hovers over the chaos in Genesis 1, that refers to the Holy Spirit.
sentences.chinese: 《创世纪》第一章盘旋在混沌之上的灵，指的是圣灵。

sentences.english: The space periodic solution and chaos of a class of infectious disease model are discussed in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文讨论一类传染病模型的空间周期解及混沌问题。

sentences.english: The simulation results showed that the inverse chaos can be controlled with this method.
sentences.chinese: 模拟结果表明，该控制法可以实现混沌的反控制。

sentences.english: The solving method for the optimal solution of the overbooking model is given based on chaos optimization algorithm.
sentences.chinese: 基于混沌优化算法给出了求解最优超订水平的方法。

sentences.english: If it was chaotic, each avalanche could swamp the brain.
sentences.chinese: 如果大脑是混沌的，每一次雪崩都能使大脑变成沼泽。

sentences.english: Welcome to the ambiguous world of service ownership.
sentences.chinese: 欢迎来到服务所有权的混沌世界。

sentences.english: An improved watermarking algorithm of odd-even quantification based on chaotic map is proposed.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一种基于混沌映射的改进奇偶量化水印算法。

sentences.english: The cloud-mussed sky turned a vague copper color.
sentences.chinese: 堆满乌云的天空现出一种混沌的紫铜色。

definition: Pangu (creator of the universe in Chinese mythology)
time immemorial/origin of the universe/the world
great emptiness/the void/heaven/the skies/universe/cosmos/original essence of the cosmos
throughout time/from ancient times (up to the present)
